{"tid":843194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【魔鬼交易】逼學生自爆月薪兼表忠 換浸大畢業禮門票兩張","createTime":"2018-10-01T03:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T08:06:32.000Z","uid":63183,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"944b63e63064541b50634c59ed7e3ebc36062f29","tid":843194,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:19:06.000Z","msg":"【魔鬼交易】畢業同學緊急呼籲，要小心填寫畢業禮門票登記報名表。當中會自動跳轉到一份問卷，強逼同學填寫月薪以至對學系、學校歸屬感，方會放行，否則冇得領取門票，雙親無法出席觀禮。<br />\n<br />\n雖然電郵聲稱問卷係不記名統計，但同學發現，問卷有一隱藏頁面，按「上一頁」會到達封面（如圖所示）。當中聲明強調問卷並非匿名，學生編號、姓名、學系、電郵皆會向調查部門披露。即係話，問卷資料唔係僅作統計調查，校方會藉此知道每個畢業生對學校嘅歸屬感等個人私隱。<br />\n<br />\n山神已去信私隱專員公署投訴。由於登記快將喺後日（3/10）截止，請即廣傳予各卒業好友，切記小心填寫問卷，切勿洩露個人資料，以防被校方秋後算帳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkbumountaingod/posts/2005066449783851\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkbumountaingod%2Fposts%2F2005066449783851&d=IY9ik%2BbGM%2BtiGt2nohrInsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f1307d49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkbumountaingod/posts/2005066449783851</a>"},{"pid":"15cd0b99d2c9fe8a50fee52fa568a6474ad7160e","tid":843194,"uid":63183,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/p7s6nq8i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp7s6nq8i&h=c6efcebc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81511d9428a273ed1212251249c548555cc599e2","tid":843194,"uid":153811,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:29:08.000Z","msg":"冇人叫你真填"},{"pid":"037780edd275a904879a0a5e50b6e52585ae873c","tid":843194,"uid":33799,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:29:48.000Z","msg":"浸會中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923292c758949b02d236fc644445721bce6cf011","tid":843194,"uid":90820,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:51:31.